{"id":"api/forms/EmailValidator","title":"EmailValidator","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/forms\", \"name\": \"@angular/forms\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/forms/EmailValidator\", \"name\": \"EmailValidator\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/forms\">@angular/forms</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L426-L478\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"emailvalidator\">EmailValidator<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator#emailvalidator\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label directive\">directive</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4uts76ebqcxgqdq19tkxaipa7\">該指令會藉助 <code><a href=\"api/forms/NG_VALIDATORS\" class=\"code-anchor\">NG_VALIDATORS</a></code> 繫結把 <code><a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a></code> 驗證器新增到任何帶有 <code><a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a></code> 屬性的控制元件上。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator#description\">檢視更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">參見<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9kcmpkcn1zt46hrz7stqgq0xa\"><a href=\"guide/form-validation\">表單驗證</a></p></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n<h2 id=\"匯出自\">匯出自<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator#匯出自\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/FormsModule\">\n      <code>FormsModule</code>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\">\n      <code>ReactiveFormsModule</code>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n  \n<section class=\"selector-list\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\">選擇器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>][<a href=\"api/forms/FormControlName\" class=\"code-anchor\">formControlName</a>]</code></li>\n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>][formControl]</code></li>\n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>][<a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a>]</code></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <a id=\"properties\"></a>\n  <h2 id=\"instance-properties\">屬性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator#instance-properties\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>屬性</th>\n        <th>說明</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"email\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"property-binding\">@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()</span><br><span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a></span>: boolean | string</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4wmhj4d3g923vyntga4jui1bc\">跟蹤繫結到該指令的 email 屬性的更改。</p>\n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"89y8yflb2bnoq4bx6j04tanqh\">電子郵件驗證基於 WHATWG HTML 規範，並進行了一些增強以包含更多 RFC\n規則。更多訊息，請參閱<a href=\"api/forms/Validators#email\">Validator.email 頁面</a>。</p>\n\n    <h3 id=\"adding-an-email-validator\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"d5q3ysjigwlb3c71y2vv0g8cv\">新增 email 驗證器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator#adding-an-email-validator\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"d4pzqo12lfve06v3prcmy61hw\">以下範例顯示如何向附加到ngModel繫結的輸入新增電子郵件驗證器。</p>\n<code-example>\n&lt;input type=\"<a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>\" name=\"<a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>\" <a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a> <a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>&gt;\n&lt;input type=\"<a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>\" name=\"<a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>\" <a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a> <a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>=\"true\"&gt;\n&lt;input type=\"<a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>\" name=\"<a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>\" <a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a> [<a href=\"api/forms/EmailValidator\" class=\"code-anchor\">email</a>]=\"true\"&gt;\n</code-example>\n\n  </section>\n\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/FormGroupName\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/NgModelGroup\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n - api/forms/Validators\n - guide/dynamic-form\n - guide/typed-forms\n - guide/update-to-version-14\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-12\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-14\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core/Input\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/EmailValidator#adding-an-email-validator\n - api/forms/EmailValidator#description\n - api/forms/EmailValidator#emailvalidator\n - api/forms/EmailValidator#instance-properties\n - api/forms/EmailValidator#see-also\n - api/forms/EmailValidator#selectors\n - api/forms/EmailValidator#匯出自\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/NG_VALIDATORS\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n - api/forms/Validators#email\n - guide/form-validation\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L426-L478\n-->"}